  2573                              ; 函数: F_HistoryUpdateTodayFromCurrent
  2574                              ; 作用: 用当前样本更新 Today 记录。
  2575 0000F966                     F_HistoryUpdateTodayFromCurrent:
  2576 0000F966 A2 00                   LDX		#C_HisRecToday
  2577 0000F968 4C 75 F9                JMP		F_HistoryUpdateRecordFromCurrent
