  2731 0000FA82 90 22                   BCC		HistoryUpdateRecord_CheckHum
  2732 0000FA84 F0 20                   BEQ		HistoryUpdateRecord_CheckHum
  2733 0000FA86                     HistoryUpdateRecord_UpdateMinNeg:
